            <description><![CDATA[<div class="quote"><blockquote><font size="2"><a href="https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&goto=findpost&pid=28237505&ptid=1101069" target="_blank"><font color="#999999">ARUCARD 发表于 2015-3-3 18:00</font></a></font><br>
听着真是凄凉，amd的东西给微软用了他有啥好处，最后还是便宜黄老板............ ...</blockquote></div><br>
1、减少单线程性能对游戏帧数的瓶颈，改善自家双模块产品线对i3的竞争力<br>
